{"tid":1323490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"破壞連儂牆係刑事毀壞！！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-16T09:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T09:28:47.000Z","uid":29081,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c098137742db99269e8ad9e3c92a0b102920a0b3","tid":1323490,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:09:10.000Z","msg":"上網見到有片有人破壞連儂牆之後同警犬講話係亂拋垃圾，呢個concept 絕對係錯嫁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一定係刑事毀壞！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例<strong>第200章 《刑事罪行條例》s.60</strong>:<br />\n<em>任何人無合法辯解而<span style=\"color: red;\">摧毀或損壞屬於他人的財產</span>，意圖摧毀或損壞該財產或罔顧該財產是否會被摧毀或損壞，即屬犯罪。</em><br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢破壞時拍片，同<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">大聲問佢牆上的memo 紙係咪屬於佢，只要唔係就係刑毀</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候就可以用<strong>第221章 《刑事訴訟程序條例》 s.101(2) </strong>將佢拘捕:<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">任何人</span>可無需手令而逮捕任何他<span style=\"color: red;\">合理地懷疑</span>犯了<span style=\"color: red;\">可逮捕的罪行</span>的人。</em><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;可逮捕的罪行&rdquo;指可處超過12個月監禁的罪行，而刑事毀壞的最高刑罰係監禁10年，所以係屬&ldquo;可逮捕的罪行&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n見到應<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">拍片同報警</span></strong>，並用《刑事訴訟程序條例》 禁止佢離開，最重要係:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要同警察講佢干犯刑事毀壞！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁咪黑警好有可能放人<br />\n<br />\n另外，如果破壞途中用咗火，係干犯<span style=\"color: red;\">縱火</span>罪，最高刑罰更加係<span style=\"color: red;\">終身監禁</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">齊做好市民！</span></span>"},{"pid":"2858820be93740b079e41dbf963966ef781a8e43","tid":1323490,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:11:37.000Z","msg":"係刑事毀壞呀！唔係亂拋垃圾！"},{"pid":"1be3b35c7f14b102c90a83835751319c9d188a0c","tid":1323490,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"要比多d 人知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf12c2e2d2d37d6e24db96b8c4e23ee6549e9ee0","tid":1323490,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"你成串內容最重要嘅刑事毀壞係咪判12個月以上係冇講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36d67db2ce6300491c7701e19952128d127d290","tid":1323490,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf12c2e2d2d37d6e24db96b8c4e23ee6549e9ee0","tid":1323490,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"你成串內容最重要嘅刑事毀壞係咪判12個月以上係冇講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"咪講咗10年囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a2797fa18125c6d3a4131ebc05acc18e53bbcc","tid":1323490,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"琴晚發左個刻骨銘心既夢，想同大家分享一下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/RtMcnU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/RtMcnU</a>"},{"pid":"139adf6b5ead5d9b3a5721ff0f59f244ed3901fe","tid":1323490,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e36d67db2ce6300491c7701e19952128d127d290","tid":1323490,"uid":29081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf12c2e2d2d37d6e24db96b8c4e23ee6549e9ee0","tid":1323490,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"你成串內容最重要嘅刑事毀壞係咪判12個月以上係冇講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"咪講咗10年囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"sorry 睇完條例就冇睇落⼀⼁⼀乛⼂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor